---

<ServiceLayout {...pageData}>
  
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Serving Abu Dhabi from Dubai</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <p>Abu Dhabi is the UAE's capital and home to federal government ministries, major corporations, and significant residential population. While our physical base is in Dubai, we serve Abu Dhabi clients with the same quality and responsiveness through our remote workflow and reliable courier delivery.</p>
        
        <p>The 90-minute drive between Dubai and Abu Dhabi means next-day delivery is straightforward. For urgent matters, same-day courier is available. Digital documents are delivered instantly, so you can have a PDF for immediate use while waiting for physical copies.</p>
        
        <h3>Why Abu Dhabi Clients Choose Us</h3>
        <p>Many Abu Dhabi residents and businesses work with Dubai-based translation services because of the concentration of MOJ-licensed translators in Dubai and the ease of remote workflow. You do not need to visit an office or make multiple trips. Send documents via WhatsApp, approve the quote, and receive your translation delivered to your door.</p>
        
        <p>For federal government submissions, court filings, or corporate documentation, our MOJ certification is valid throughout the UAE. There is no difference in acceptance between translation done in Dubai and Abu Dhabi—MOJ licensing is federal.</p>
        
        <h3>Understanding Abu Dhabi's Distinct Needs</h3>
        <p>Abu Dhabi has its own governmental structure alongside the federal ministries headquartered there. ADJD (Abu Dhabi Judicial Department) handles local court matters. Abu Dhabi DED manages local business licensing. ADGM operates as a separate financial free zone under common law. We understand these distinctions and advise appropriately.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Federal Government and Ministry Documents</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <h3>Working with Federal Authorities</h3>
        <p>Many UAE federal ministries are headquartered in Abu Dhabi: Ministry of Foreign Affairs, Ministry of Interior, Ministry of Human Resources and Emiratisation, and others. Documents for these ministries—whether personal immigration matters, employment documentation, or official correspondence—require MOJ-certified translation.</p>
        
        <p>We translate documents for federal authority submissions regularly and understand the terminology and formatting expectations. Whether you are dealing with visa matters, employment permits, or official applications, we provide translations that meet federal standards.</p>
        
        <h3>Immigration and Visa Documents</h3>
        <p>Abu Dhabi residents processing visa applications, family sponsorship, or <a href="/services/golden-visa-translation/">Golden Visa</a> applications need translated documents for federal immigration authorities. <a href="/personal/vital-records/birth/">Birth certificates</a>, <a href="/personal/vital-records/marriage/">marriage certificates</a>, <a href="/personal/education/degree/">degree certificates</a>, and other supporting documents all require MOJ-certified translation.</p>
        
        <h3>Employment Documentation</h3>
        <p>MOHRE processing for Abu Dhabi-based employees follows the same federal requirements as elsewhere in the UAE. <a href="/services/certificate-translation/">Certificate translation</a> for work permits, salary certificate translation, and employment contract translation all meet MOHRE standards.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Abu Dhabi Judicial Department (ADJD)</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <h3>Court Documents and Legal Filings</h3>
        <p>ADJD handles civil, criminal, and personal status cases in Abu Dhabi. Court filings, evidence documents, and legal submissions may require translation. We provide MOJ-certified translations that ADJD accepts for all court proceedings.</p>
        
        <p>For <a href="/services/legal-translation/">legal translation</a> involving Abu Dhabi courts, we work with individuals and law firms to meet court deadlines and formatting requirements. Urgent court filings can be accommodated with our Express and VIP Concierge services.</p>
        
        <h3>Personal Status Matters</h3>
        <p>Divorce proceedings, custody matters, and inheritance cases in Abu Dhabi require translated documents when parties or evidence involve foreign elements. Marriage certificates, birth certificates, foreign court orders, and other civil documents need certified translation for court submission.</p>
        
        <h3>Commercial Litigation</h3>
        <p>Business disputes before Abu Dhabi courts may involve contracts, correspondence, and corporate documents in languages other than Arabic. We translate commercial documentation for litigation support, working with law firms on volume and deadline requirements.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>ADGM Corporate Services</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <h3>Abu Dhabi Global Market</h3>
        <p>ADGM is Abu Dhabi's financial free zone, operating under English common law similar to <a href="/locations/dubai/difc/">DIFC</a> in Dubai. Companies registered in ADGM use English as the primary operating language, with documentation following common law conventions.</p>
        
        <p>ADGM entities may need Arabic translation when dealing with mainland Abu Dhabi authorities, opening bank accounts with UAE banks, or engaging in property transactions. We translate ADGM corporate documents to Arabic with awareness of common law concepts and their Arabic equivalents.</p>
        
        <h3>ADGM Courts</h3>
        <p>ADGM operates its own courts under English common law. Proceedings occur primarily in English, but Arabic documents introduced as evidence require certified translation. We support ADGM court filings with translations that meet court requirements.</p>
        
        <h3>Financial Services Regulatory Authority (FSRA)</h3>
        <p>ADGM's FSRA regulates financial services within the free zone. Regulatory correspondence, license applications, and compliance documents may require translation when dealing with other regulatory bodies or for record-keeping purposes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Abu Dhabi Districts We Serve</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <h3>Abu Dhabi City</h3>
        <p>The central city area including Corniche, Al Khalidiyah, and the downtown districts. Government offices, courts, and major businesses are concentrated here. Next-day delivery is standard; same-day available for urgent matters.</p>
        
        <h3>Al Reem Island</h3>
        <p>A major residential and commercial development with significant professional population. Many corporate offices and residential towers. Regular delivery service with same next-day timing.</p>
        
        <h3>Saadiyat Island</h3>
        <p>Cultural district with museums, universities, and upscale residential. NYU Abu Dhabi and Louvre Abu Dhabi create international community with diverse translation needs. Standard delivery service.</p>
        
        <h3>Yas Island</h3>
        <p>Entertainment and residential district. Growing residential population and hospitality businesses. Included in standard Abu Dhabi delivery area.</p>
        
        <h3>Al Ain</h3>
        <p>Abu Dhabi's second city, inland near the Omani border. University town with significant population. Delivery available with slightly extended timeline.</p>
        
        <h3>Western Region</h3>
        <p>Including areas like Madinat Zayed and Liwa. Delivery available; timing confirmed based on specific location.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Service Levels</h2>
      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>Standard</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">From AED 150</div>
          <p class="pricing-time">24-hour + next-day delivery</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>MOJ-certified translation</li>
            <li>Digital PDF immediately</li>
            <li>Next-day Abu Dhabi courier</li>
            <li>WhatsApp updates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card pricing-card--featured">
          <h3>Express</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">From AED 300</div>
          <p class="pricing-time">6-hour + same-day courier</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Everything in Standard</li>
            <li>Priority processing</li>
            <li>Same-day Abu Dhabi delivery</li>
            <li>Court deadline support</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>VIP Concierge</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">From AED 500</div>
          <p class="pricing-time">1-hour draft + urgent courier</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Everything in Express</li>
            <li>Immediate assignment</li>
            <li>Draft within 60 minutes</li>
            <li>Urgent courier dispatch</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Getting Started</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <p>Send your documents via WhatsApp from anywhere in Abu Dhabi. We will review them, confirm the translation requirements, and provide a quote. Once approved, work begins immediately.</p>
        
        <p>For federal ministry submissions, court filings, or ADGM matters, tell us the intended use so we can advise on any additional requirements like <a href="/services/attestation/">attestation</a> or specific formatting.</p>
        
        <p>Digital copies are delivered as soon as translation is complete. Physical copies ship the same day by courier, arriving next day to Abu Dhabi addresses. For urgent matters, same-day courier delivery can be arranged.</p>
        
        <p>There is no need to visit Dubai. Our complete workflow—document submission, payment, delivery—happens remotely. You get the same quality and service as Dubai-based clients with the convenience of delivery to your Abu Dhabi address.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <InlineCallout 
        type="tip" 
        title="Federal Authority Documents"
        link="/services/attestation/mofa/"
        linkText="MOFA attestation services"
      >
        Documents for federal ministries in Abu Dhabi often require MOFA attestation along with translation.
      </InlineCallout>

      <RelatedServices 
        pageKey="abuDhabi"
        title="Common Document Needs"
        maxItems={6}
      />
      
      <CrossSiloLinks 
        pageKey="abuDhabi"
        title="Other Locations"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

</ServiceLayout>

<style>
  .content-prose {
    max-width: 800px;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  
  .content-prose h3 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }
  
  .content-prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }
  
  .content-prose a {
    color: var(--accent-color);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  .content-prose a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
  
  .pricing-grid { 
    display: grid; 
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); 
    gap: 1.5rem; 
  }
  
  .pricing-card { 
    background: #ffffff; 
    border-radius: 1rem; 
    padding: 2rem; 
    text-align: center; 
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); 
  }
  
  .pricing-card--featured { 
    border-color: var(--accent-color); 
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(255, 22, 84, 0.15); 
  }
  
  .pricing-card h3 { 
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem; 
    font-size: 1.25rem; 
  }
  
  .pricing-price { 
    font-size: 2rem; 
    font-weight: 700; 
    color: var(--primary-color); 
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .pricing-time { 
    color: var(--text-muted); 
    font-size: 0.9rem; 
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .pricing-features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: left;
  }
  
  .pricing-features li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  
  .pricing-features li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
